Getting Started
------------------------------------------

To install a required library on ubuntu

$ sudo apt-get install freeglut3-dev

To compile MATPLOT++ library, type as following:

$ tar xvf matplotpp-0.3.x.tar
$ cd matplotpp
$ make

To compile examples:

$ cd examples
$ make
